ygData.messageBody:
I am traveling to oasis from qeynos. I am a lev 17 warrior and have never
been much past high pass, so any advice would be appreciated. Also I am
looking for a good group to team up with over there for a bit,, want to get
a better two handed weapon (I have a fine steel t-h sword) or better armor
(have full banded). Anyway, if anyone wants to team or travel with me send
me a note.

Arathorne,
Warrior of Solsek Ro
